data.name: Triple Tactic Tasking
data.desc: If your opponent has activated a monster effect this turn: Set 1 Normal Spell/Trap directly from your Deck, except "Triple Tactic Tasking" (it cannot be activated this turn), or, if your opponent controls a monster, you can add that card to your hand instead. You can only activate 1 "Triple Tactic Tasking" per turn.
